  <Markdown>
## 3. No Templates (Raw JSON)

Without preview/detail attributes, Navigator shows raw item data:
  </Markdown>

  <Navigator id="raw_navigator" title="Raw Data View" searchable="false">
- id: item_a
  title: First Item
  category: Category A
  value: 100

- id: item_b
  title: Second Item
  category: Category B
  value: 200
  </Navigator>

  <Markdown>
## How It Works

1. **YAML Content**: Items defined as YAML list in block text
2. **Template References**: `preview` and `detail` attributes point to block IDs
3. **Data as Props**: All item fields passed as attributes to templates
4. **Search**: Filters by name, title, role, or description fields
5. **State**: Selected item and search query persisted in Redux
  </Markdown>

